{"id":15544,"date":"2022-12-31T04:13:26","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:13:26","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-azure.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:13:26","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:13:26","slug":"xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-azure-2","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-azure-2\/","title":{"rendered":"Xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe trong khoang l\u00e1i Bentley Azure"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<ul class=\"social_left\">\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"myvne_save_for_later\" data-token=\"5cbdb55b43c237ab4a83d7c254df2cb1\" data-article-id=\"4527225\" title=\"L\u01b0u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft\">\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li_comment\"><span class=\"number_cmt txt_num_comment num_cmt_detail\" data-type=\"comment\" data-objecttype=\"7\" data-objectid=\"4527225\"><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span class=\"tip\">Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1536x768.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x300.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x49.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x167.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x125.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x98.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_884_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Bentley trong ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4.  Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m xa x\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng xe Anh Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Azure v\u1edbi c\u00e1c t\u00ednh n\u0103ng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch b\u00ean trong cabin.<\/p>\n<p>D\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Azure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bentley \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean Bentayga, sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 Flying Spur, Continental GT, Continental GTC v\u00e0 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Bentayga EWB.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x94.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x320.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x240.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1536x480.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x188.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_694_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450446_468_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng kh\u00e1i ni\u1ec7m \u201cs\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe sau tay l\u00e1i\u201d, nh\u00f3m c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Bentley\u2019s Azure \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eddi nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7n kinh h\u1ecdc Katherine Templar-Lewis, \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Katherine Studios.  Sau khi nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0 th\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i trong xe, nh\u00e0 khoa h\u1ecdc n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p d\u1eef li\u1ec7u t\u1eeb Bentley, \u0111\u01b0a ra ph\u00e2n t\u00edch v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n khi ng\u1ed3i b\u00ean trong cabin xe, d\u00f9 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0o.  l\u00e1i xe ho\u1eb7c h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch.<\/p>\n<p>Theo \u0111\u00f3, hai y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 NVH (Noise \u2013 ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, Vibration \u2013 \u0111\u1ed9 rung, Harshness \u2013 s\u1ed1c).  Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u n\u00e0y, theo d\u00f5i h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong kho\u1ea3ng 4 n\u0103m, cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac v\u1edbi ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n giao th\u00f4ng tr\u00ean 70 db c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh tr\u1ea7m c\u1ea3m cao h\u01a1n 65%.  L\u1ea5y Bentley Bentayga EWB phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure l\u00e0m v\u00ed d\u1ee5, d\u1eef li\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y xe v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh \u00eam h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb 4-26%, t\u00f9y thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o t\u1ea7n su\u1ea5t v\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i b\u00ean trong.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" title=\"1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_208_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>S\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe khi di chuy\u1ec3n \u2013 xe c\u00e0ng \u00eam th\u00ec h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.  \u1ede t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1eddng trung b\u00ecnh, d\u1ea3i t\u1ea7n t\u1edbi h\u1ea1n 5 Hz \u2013 20 Hz, chi\u1ebfc SUV c\u1ee7a Bentley c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 rung th\u1ee9 c\u1ea5p khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n 27% so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, theo nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u si\u00eau sang.  Anh trai.<\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4i th\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 Bentley thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc (Science Infored Design), s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean xe Bentley.  .  Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 s\u01b0 \u00e2m thanh th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c tri\u1ec7t ti\u00eau ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n, \u0111\u1ed9 rung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eadt.  Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Bentley t\u1eadp trung nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u00e0o thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m ti\u1ebfng \u1ed3n g\u00e2y m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, mang \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u201cbi\u1ec7t l\u1eadp\u201d v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng gian b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i.<\/p>\n<p>Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u khoa h\u1ecdc v\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng khi l\u00e1i xe, Andy Jackson, k\u1ef9 s\u01b0 \u00e2m thanh c\u1ee7a Bentley chia s\u1ebb c\u00e1ch t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i hi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng v\u1edbi \u00e2m thanh r\u1ed3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i \u00e2m thanh th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean l\u00ean xe Bentley. \u00c2m thanh ph\u00e1t ra t\u1eeb xe \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng, c\u00e1ch ly ng\u01b0\u1eddi ng\u1ed3i trong xe v\u1edbi th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf t\u1ea1p \u00e2m b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o cabin. \u00c2m thanh h\u00e0i h\u00f2a v\u1edbi c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 c\u1ea3m quan kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean xe\u201d.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_239_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" title=\"1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x243.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x831.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x623.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x487.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_664_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>Gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i \u00eam \u00e1i khi\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c l\u00e1i v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n xe c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.  V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure c\u1ee7a Bentley \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb Front Seat Comfort Specification gi\u00fap \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 th\u1ebf t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure c\u1ee7a Bentley \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trang b\u1ecb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gh\u1ebf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh 22 h\u01b0\u1edbng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i cao tr\u00ean 1,9 m ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi 1,5 m.  Ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 massage c\u00f3 6 m\u1ee9c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t gi\u00fap t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.  B\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec7n 2 b\u00ean, d\u00e2y an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh theo \u00fd mu\u1ed1n.<\/p>\n<p>H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n thanh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng 48V (Bentley Dynamic Ride) tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i v\u00e0 h\u00e0nh kh\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u1ecbch chuy\u1ec3n v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ng\u1ed3i qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1edd c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed ph\u00e2n t\u00e1ch c\u00e1c thanh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.  C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u00f4-men xo\u1eafn l\u00ean t\u1edbi 1.300 Nm trong 0,3 gi\u00e2y khi xe v\u00e0o cua, nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, theo c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb Bentley.<\/p>\n<p>T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n g\u00f3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e1i xe Touring Spectification, bao g\u1ed3m H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 giao th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 B\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Bentley \u2013 m\u1ed9t camera c\u00f3 radar theo d\u00f5i t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng giao th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng x\u00e1.  \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o v\u00e0 ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba tai n\u1ea1n.  H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh th\u00edch \u1ee9ng gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch v\u1edbi xe ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x154.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x525.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x394.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1536x787.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x308.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_908_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh HUD c\u00f3 ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u00ecn \u0111\u00eam, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng camera h\u1ed3ng ngo\u1ea1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn di\u1ec7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i b\u1ed9, xe \u0111\u1ea1p hay \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u1eadt th\u00f4ng qua ch\u00f9m s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e8n c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 LED.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ean, Bentley x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u00e0 h\u00e3ng xe \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi ti\u00ean phong trong xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i Bentley t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x43.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x147.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x110.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x86.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_104_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1060w\"><\/p>\n<p>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn M\u00e0u s\u1eafc v\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Bentley Motors, Maria Mulder, cho bi\u1ebft d\u00f2ng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Azure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7n kinh h\u1ecdc, gi\u00fap h\u00e3ng hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u v\u00e0 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc.  , x\u00fac gi\u00e1c v\u00e0 m\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng\u2026 trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p>Maria Mulder cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cKhi ch\u00fang ta nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u00f9 ho\u1eb7c m\u00e0u s\u1eafc d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, n\u00e3o ti\u1ebft ra c\u00e1c ch\u1ea5t h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc nh\u01b0 dopamine khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu. C\u00e1c th\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e1c k\u00edch th\u00edch v\u1eadt l\u00fd, g\u00e2y ra nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong n\u00e3o v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh\u201d.  \u201cM\u1ecdi y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u, \u00e2m thanh, chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ea3nh, m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, x\u00fac gi\u00e1c\u2026 \u0111\u1ec1u t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ea7n kinh. V\u00ec v\u1eady cabin Azure \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ch\u1ec9n chu nh\u1ea5t.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u00ean, n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Bentley Azure \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt Wellness Quilting, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng mi\u1ebfng da h\u00ecnh kim c\u01b0\u01a1ng, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u01b0\u01a1ng quan gi\u1eefa \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1i.  C\u00e1c t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u bao g\u1ed3m Dark Walnut, Crown-cut Walnut v\u00e0 Koa \u2013 v\u1edbi l\u1edbp ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.  Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1eb7t phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn 15 m\u00e0u da n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, ph\u1ed1i m\u00e0u ch\u1ec9 th\u00eau, vi\u1ec1n gh\u1ebf h\u00ecnh \u1ed1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n\u2026 Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea3ng t\u00e1p-l\u00f4 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh xoay \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a Bentley, \u0111\u00e8n vi\u1ec1n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t t\u00f9y ch\u1ec9nh.  t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng, v\u00f4 l\u0103ng hai t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u c\u00f3 s\u01b0\u1edfi.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x122.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x416.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x312.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1536x624.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x244.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_844_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i Bentley t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft, Bentayga EWB l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m cao c\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t trong c\u00e1c bi\u1ebfn th\u1ec3 Azure.  H\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a m\u1eabu xe n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Airline Seat Spectification h\u1ea1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng gia, \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 4+1.  Gh\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh 22 h\u01b0\u1edbng, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t kh\u00ed h\u1eadu t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o.<\/p>\n<p>\u1ede ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 Relax, h\u00e0ng gh\u1ebf sau c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ea3 40 \u0111\u1ed9, b\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e2n b\u1ecdc da.  \u1ede ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 Business, l\u01b0ng gh\u1ebf th\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng t\u1ea1o t\u01b0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i khi di chuy\u1ec3n.  V\u1edbi t\u00ednh n\u0103ng Seat Auto Climate, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn 6 m\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111o nhi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed9 ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac, \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t\u2026 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u.<\/p>\n<p>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh t\u01b0 th\u1ebf Postural Adjusment s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec7m h\u01a1i \u00f4m s\u00e1t \u0111\u00f9i, t\u1ef1a vai, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p th\u00eam \u0111\u1ec7m kh\u00ed massage l\u01b0ng gi\u00fap thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u00ecnh d\u00e1ng gh\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3i t\u1ecfa c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1eafp c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.  T\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bentley m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ba ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c nhau, c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf tr\u1ee5c v\u00edt 3D, 6 v\u00f9ng \u00e1p su\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp t\u1ea1o ra 177 c\u00e1ch \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh sau m\u1ed7i 3 gi\u1edd.  Nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1eeb h\u00e3ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng gh\u1ebf ng\u1ed3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh th\u00f4ng minh gi\u00fap c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung.<\/p>\n<p>\u201cN\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Azure c\u1ee7a Bentley h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng gian gi\u00e0u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac, gi\u00fap ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam sinh l\u1ef1c, l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n cho kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n cho bi\u1ebft.  Nh\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i Bentley t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft.<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">N\u1ed9i dung: Quang Anh \u2013 <span style=\"text-align:left;\">T\u1ea5m h\u00ecnh:<\/span> <span style=\"text-align:left;\">Bentley \u2013 Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf: Th\u00e1i H\u00f9ng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg\" title=\"1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-300x125.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1024x427.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-768x320.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-1536x640.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley-600x250.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672450447_636_xu-huong-cham-soc-suc-khoe-trong-khoang-lai-bentley.jpg 1920w\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i Hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00e0i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Bentley trong ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4. Tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m xa x\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng xe Anh Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0a l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi, b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch thi\u1ebft l\u1eadp xu h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":15545,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15544"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15544"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15544\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/15545"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15544"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15544"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15544"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}